     H            Y.
     F** AB#R75 ********************************************
     F*   ..  KANBAN READIGN DATA FILE REFORMATION  ..     *
     F*       K.OKACHI                    1998.03.18       *
     F* TCHK1 04/12/07 ADD AB#WP77 FOR TRACE               *
JW1  F* JW    06/02/16 STOP DELETING WHEN "D"              *
     F******************************************************
     FAB#PP10 IP  E                    DISK
     FAB#WP75 O   E                    DISK
TCHK1FAB#WP77 O   E                    DISK
     F******************************************************
     I            DS
     I                                        1   80BANOHZ
     I                                        1   40BANOYY
     I                                        5   60BANOMM
     I                                        7   80BANODD
      *
     I            DS
     I                                        1   80BASKHZ
     I                                        1   40BASKYY
     I                                        5   60BASKMM
     I                                        7   80BASKDD
     I            DS
     I                                        1   80BAURHZ
     I                                        1   40BAURYY
     I                                        5   60BAURMM
     I                                        7   80BAURDD
     I            DS
     I                                        1   80WHIZK
     I                                        1   40WYY
     I                                        5   60WMM
     I                                        7   80WDD
     I            DS
     I                                        1   80YYMMDD
     I                                        1   40NEN
     I                                        5   60TUKI
     I                                        7   80HI
     I******************************************************
      *
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           PHIZK   8
     C                     PARM           PRECD   7
     C                     PARM           PKENS   7
     C                     MOVE PHIZK     WHIZK   80
      *
     C                     ADD  1         WRECD   70
      *
     C**JW1      BASKJY    IFEQ 'D'
     C**         BASKHZ    ANDLE*DATE
TCHK1C**                   WRITEAB#WP771
     C**                   GOTO NDAT
     C**                   ENDIF
      *
     C           BANOHZ    IFGT WHIZK
     C           BAURHZ    OREQ 0
      *
     C                     Z-ADDWYY       NEN     40
     C                     Z-ADDWMM       TUKI    20
     C                     Z-ADDWDD       HI      20
     C                     SUB  2         TUKI
      *
     C           TUKI      IFLE 0
     C                     SUB  1         NEN
     C                     ADD  12        TUKI
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C           BANOHZ    IFLT YYMMDD
TCHK1C                     WRITEAB#WP771
     C                     GOTO NDAT
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     ADD  1         WKENS   70
     C                     WRITEAB#WP751
TCHK1C                     ELSE
TCHK1C                     WRITEAB#WP771
     C                     ENDIF
     C           NDAT      TAG
      *
     CLR                   MOVE WRECD     PRECD
     CLR                   MOVE WKENS     PKENS
